    <abstract id="aspace_675d8d5c4fc75820e9aa85d7de19fe71" label="Abstract">This collection contains miscellaneous records of Congregation Kether Torah (Pittsburgh, Pa.), including: history, charter, by-laws, membership lists from c. 1960, minutes of eight congregational meetings between 1927 and 1939, papers concerning the sale of the synagogue property in the Hill District, blueprint and legal documents concerning cemetery in Reserve Township, Pa., some general correspondence and a blueprint of synagogue from c. 1913.</abstract>
